 we are able to raise capital from our individual investor base for the businesses in our portfolio we work with senior management to develop both an operating strategy and capital plan for growing the company’s business and creating value for its shareholders by utilizing the experience of our founders and principals we help senior management teams find the best financial solutions for their companies we are an active merchant banking partner for your business extensive operating experience our team includes ceos and cfos of businesses ranging from startups to multibillion dollar nyse companies we have a successful track record as operators of portfolio companies our advisory board has diverse management experience experienced management team we have extensive experience at many different types and sizes of companies and firms our dedicated team of professionals work together for each client we are financial services and health care focused access to alternative sources of capital our firm’s own capital high net worth investor base iroquois financial partners    back to top  west end avenue suite  nashville tn  phone  fax infoiroquoiscgcom investments are made available and offered through our brokerdealer iroquois capital advisors llc a wholly owned subsidiary and finra and sipc member business continuity plan privacy policy usa patriot act iroquois  iroquois capital nominates two highly qualified directors for election to the lrad board  the business journals menu select a city national albany albuquerque atlanta austin baltimore birmingham boston buffalo charlotte chicago cincinnati columbus dallas dayton denver greensborowinstonsalem honolulu houston jacksonville kansas city los angeles louisville memphis miamifort lauderdale milwaukee minneapolisst paul nashville new york orlando philadelphia phoenix pittsburgh portland raleighdurham sacramento san antonio san francisco seattle silicon valley st louis tampa bay washington dc wichita limited time offer subscrib